column2:
"Back already, I see. Were you successful?
The real Kyokuya already gave her a cookie?!"

"Ridiculous! I could never be so honest!
Gh... Could this be the work of an enemy 《Phantom》?"
"Hmph, so there was no need for me after all...? But if he planned to repay her himself, why embody me..."

"What's that? Xiera was the one who embodied me?
That little meddler...!"

"Well, no matter...
As thanks for your assistance, I give you this."

"Hmph, am I finally being honest?
Don't misunderstand me.
You have the \"Black Wolf's\" thanks, nothing more."

"I'm speaking honestly at last...?
Impertinent fool! Begone from my sight!"
